The paper deals with computational cartography and label placement in maps, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also discusses algorithms and models for map labeling, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments conducted in the paper involve processing and analyzing OpenStreetMap data, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) and data structures (cs.DS).
